nodes.text: 2017 Topps Journey to Star Wars: The Last Jedi

The 2017 Topps Journey to Star Wars: The Last Jedi will be published by Topps and released as part of Lucasfilm's Journey to Star Wars: The Last Jedi publishing program in advance of the theatrical release of the film Star Wars: The Last Jedi.
